    <item>
      <title>债券交易员迎来重要的一周，他们的赌注大获成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/bond-traders-greet-a-momentous-week-with-their-wagers-reeled-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在连续数周推高美国国债收益率后，交易员们纷纷在美国大选之前撤出筹码，由于总统大选结果难分胜负，他们不愿在债券市场上进行大胆押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/bond-traders-greet-a-momentous-week-with-their-wagers-reeled-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 17:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>原油价格低迷，OPEC+ 再次推迟恢复供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/opec-has-agreement-in-principle-to-delay-december-ouput-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+同意将12月份的增产计划推迟一个月，这是由于脆弱的经济前景和油价持续挣扎，该组织第二次推迟恢复供应的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/opec-has-agreement-in-principle-to-delay-december-ouput-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 15:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑坦德银行英国子公司多年落后后面临新打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/santander-s-uk-unit-faces-new-hit-after-years-of-lagging-behind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桑坦德银行对其英国业务的不满日益加深，裁员和上周昂贵的汽车金融审查只是高管们面临的最新麻烦，因为他们更加重视其他国家的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/santander-s-uk-unit-faces-new-hit-after-years-of-lagging-behind</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 15:06:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特的“蓝点”奥马哈享受总统聚光灯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/buffett-s-blue-dot-omaha-relishing-the-presidential-spotlight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥马哈以其美味的牛排和亿万富翁沃伦·巴菲特的故乡而闻名。但这个周末，当地人正享受着美国总统聚光灯下的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/buffett-s-blue-dot-omaha-relishing-the-presidential-spotlight</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西财政部长应卢拉要求取消欧洲之行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/brazil-s-finance-chief-cancels-trip-to-europe-at-lula-s-request</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于雷亚尔持续下跌且政府考虑的削减开支幅度存在不确定性，巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 取消了本周的欧洲之行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/brazil-s-finance-chief-cancels-trip-to-europe-at-lula-s-request</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举焦虑笼罩新兴市场 投资者纷纷降低风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/election-anxiety-grips-emerging-markets-as-investors-slash-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从墨西哥城到上海，经历了动荡之年的贸易商们正准备迎接新的政治冲击：美国总统大选有可能颠覆全球贸易，并可能扰乱发展中国家的经济前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/election-anxiety-grips-emerging-markets-as-investors-slash-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街的目光聚焦于选举，而其资金却不那么关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/wall-street-s-eyes-are-on-the-election-its-money-not-so-much</link>
      <description><![CDATA[还剩一个交易日。周二美国选民将选出下一任总统，这可能会决定未来四年的经济走向，华尔街在周二之前只剩下这些了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/wall-street-s-eyes-are-on-the-election-its-money-not-so-much</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 13:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PIF 入股中东最大广播公司 股价上涨 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/middle-east-s-top-broadcaster-jumps-10-as-saudi-pif-buys-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在沙特阿拉伯主权财富基金同意以约 20 亿美元的价格从政府手中收购中东最大的广播公司多数股权后，该公司股价在沙特阿拉伯飙升 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/middle-east-s-top-broadcaster-jumps-10-as-saudi-pif-buys-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 08:39:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周美国大选后，美联储及其同行将继续降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/fed-and-peers-will-go-ahead-with-rate-cuts-after-this-week-s-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们普遍预计，美联储和许多富裕国家的同行将在下周再次降低利率，此时正值美国总统大选尚未决出结果之时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/fed-and-peers-will-go-ahead-with-rate-cuts-after-this-week-s-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 20:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
